{"tid":2200638,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官派律師剝奪辯護 知情權","createTime":"2020-09-13T06:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T06:23:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"04f6550e9a2f9bbc6f24a60c487ac39774160f16","tid":2200638,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/OUEFICNYVVFYPJVELHLWWJ2PG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FOUEFICNYVVFYPJVELHLWWJ2PG4%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513SuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=d06fc37f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FOUEFICNYVVFYPJVELHLWWJ2PG4%2F&h=7321f7b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/OUEFICNYVVFYPJVELHLWWJ2PG4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官派律師剝奪辯護 知情權<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】官派律師在內地敏感案件不時出現，最近湖南公益組織長沙富能案三名被告被指顛覆國家政權罪，三人失蹤一年多，同樣被指派官派律師。家人和委託的律師一直得不到消息，直到近日他們到法院維權，衝突中由警員致電法官詢問才得知案件已經秘密開庭，該案其中一名被告程淵的律師對本報表示，官派律師的出現不單剝奪了辯護權，甚至連家屬的知情權都奪去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/36BFaR5IrP9mhwmkj66euY_JHzw=/1365x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PUVNA3CSMVGS7NPGDDL7ES766E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F36BFaR5IrP9mhwmkj66euY_JHzw%3D%2F1365x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPUVNA3CSMVGS7NPGDDL7ES766E.jpg&h=40f06142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧思位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n王全璋：當局五派律師逼認罪<br />\n<br />\n公益組織長沙富能的案件中三名被告被捕了一年，家屬對於案情一直不知情，謝燕益指，官派律師和官方配合得非常完美，不單剝奪了家屬的辯護權，連知情權都剝奪了。<br />\n<br />\n另一名709律師王全璋今年4月獲釋。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n王全璋說自己被拘留期間一共被官方安排五個律師，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被強行安排官派律師的維權律師謝陽也對本報指，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n代理港人案件的盧思位在昨港人家屬記者。。。。。"}]}